snippet.title: Isles Of Krom  - Join the playtest
snippet.description:
Journey through the tainted Isles of Krom and be part of the team crafting the next Souls-Action Roguelike.

Official website: https://www.IslesOfKrom.com
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1490990/Isles_of_Krom/
